com.deltaxml.pipe.filters.dx2.wbw

Class DeltaSpaceElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.deltaxml.pipe.filters.dx2.wbw.WordByWordElement
      • com.deltaxml.pipe.filters.dx2.wbw.DeltaSpaceElement

  • public class DeltaSpaceElement
extends WordByWordElement

    A representation of a space element used by WordBufferingFilter and its sub-types to represent and manipulate the buffer of word/space/punctuation elements. This class is useful if you're creating an outfilter which is processing word/space/punctuation elements.
